{"tid":815784,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ps4 fifa 18及19 pro club比賽球會招收合拍隊友","createTime":"2018-09-12T09:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T11:54:32.000Z","uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71b62323b6d55c650be69fe0c3b9389a973a9944","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"我地球會組軍幾個月後嘗試參加vpl s19<br />\n可惜人數不足 銀盃8強止步<br />\n<br />\n球會簡介<br />\n。每晚大概2200-0100開波<br />\n。以4321/433為主要陣式<br />\n。以快速防反為主<br />\n。所以需要大家現位走位<br />\n<br />\n現希望招到更多full time 隊友參加來屆比賽：<br />\n。1名同時可駕馭柱躉及靈巧型前鋒<br />\n。2名側翼<br />\n。數名防中<br />\n。數名閘及中後衛<br />\n。1名龍門<br />\n<br />\n隊友要求：<br />\n。Full time 隊友<br />\n。每星期出席4-5日 (part time暫不考慮）<br />\n。打機時會開mic交流 營造良好氣氛<br />\n。互相尊重對方<br />\n<br />\n麻煩有興趣同我地夾下嘅tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/Eyikea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FEyikea&d=LQWnglECIL2He5N2i7ZqgAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b9732e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Eyikea</a>"},{"pid":"779d1616da8a0ad0d4f715daf6075536010975b9","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"05257a6435397033bd390d69483cdf696c25c4ef","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"Push 招中後場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df704489d3f06d5ea0fe64a8e27bad82fb99aa6","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05257a6435397033bd390d69483cdf696c25c4ef","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"Push 招中後場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f20fd1d8db9457d49ca061b4dbffa94714093b4","tid":815784,"uid":197124,"like":0,"disli